Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒想到第一次穿婚紗是工作需要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.67,0:02:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前覺得自己在此之前就已經結婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結婚慾望很強呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.84,0:02:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.76,0:02:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但總覺得像這樣努力著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.18,0:02:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天能遇到我的白馬王子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.69,0:02:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  製作人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.78,0:02:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件禮服馬上就要換掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.86,0:03:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  午休後就要換別的衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要我幫忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.58,0:03:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是發給朋友而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.98,0:03:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(60,20)\fs18}「我要奔向幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.98,0:03:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(135,40)\fs18}真抱歉  其實我下個月28號就要結婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.98,0:03:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(83,60)\fs18}雖然說好不會偷跑的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.98,0:03:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(50,80)\fs18}真的很抱歉」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣…發送
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友美一定會嚇一跳的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  友美
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.23,0:03:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用這麼驚訝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.94,0:03:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算結婚又有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙你的騙你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實只是結婚雜誌的模特兒而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次見面再好好聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該馬上就能請到假了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.58,0:03:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…我什麼時候走到這裡來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:03:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  您掉東西…了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.35,0:04:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  找到新娘了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.31,0:04:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻就過去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  回婚禮現場了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.77,0:04:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…還有攝影…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓小姐到哪裡去打電話了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.82,0:04:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便當都已經來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.29,0:04:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是梓小姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.88,0:04:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.80,0:04:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製作人！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓…梓小姐被拐走了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我親眼看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.39,0:04:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.01,0:04:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是梓的手機
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.06,0:04:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製作人  現在立刻就去救人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美希  我們會盡快回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:04:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幫我們拖延下時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美希我會試試的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們明白您不願意和從未相識的人結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們的主人是很了不起的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您也一定會滿意的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之立刻回到婚禮現場
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.83,0:05:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…請問是不是認錯人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是三浦梓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要穿那麼容易混淆的衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得了  是結婚戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得還給那位新娘才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  工作室那邊也要回去一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:06:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  我到底是從哪裡過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不幹  這種父母間決定的婚事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打死都不幹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.43,0:06:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣說  我們主人也是打心底想要娶您
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.77,0:06:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都把先祖代代相傳的傳家寶戒送您了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.52,0:06:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這正是其證明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種戒指還你就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.27,0:06:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉哪兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.49,0:06:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.41,0:06:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來…剛才那人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.62,0:06:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會錯的  是傳家寶戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快回去找
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手機也掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼去工作室…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  坐計程車就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  我想問一下路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我離開村莊來這裡見兒子但卻迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.57,0:07:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去那個叫Land  Land  Tower的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那地方好像…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.37,0:07:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該就在那
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真對不起  我也在趕路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你幫忙了  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是先帶您去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.82,0:07:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製作人  再快點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.41,0:07:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別強人所難了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你太快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那輛車…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:08:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製作人  就是那輛車拐走梓小姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.87,0:08:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計程車
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請跟著前面那輛車
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.59,0:08:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是警察什麼的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是藝人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住  把梓小姐帶哪兒去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓？是剛才那人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.14,0:08:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些人也在找戒指嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在車站目擊到穿著婚紗的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員立即前往
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解  趕快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓戒指被搶了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住  誘拐犯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.04,0:08:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真  很危險的  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請給我發票
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.63,0:08:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標從車站前往中華街
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員立即前往
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  我也一起找
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我帶路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.43,0:08:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:08:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別廢話  帶我去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.14,0:09:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉  我忘記自己也是路盲了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  我一個人肯定也會迷路的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.44,0:09:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  俊嗣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.20,0:09:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  沒迷路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說在那個Land  Land  Tower碰面的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是約好在這個Marine  Port  Tower等嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.16,0:09:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是您帶母親過來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.66,0:09:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道該怎麼辦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.96,0:09:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡哪裡  只是路盲碰巧走對路而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.90,0:09:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你添麻煩了  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.94,0:09:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老婆婆也保重
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我也要快點找輛計程車
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:09:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩個孩子的母親在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解  發現後立即確保
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.14,0:10:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有消息說在肉包子店目擊到那女的了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是剛才那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不會把梓小姐交給你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.74,0:10:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很燙要當心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.29,0:10:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好  我也想讓她吹吹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.54,0:10:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去買肉包
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs22}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.59,0:10:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.84,0:10:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.84,0:10:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我肉包
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.46,0:10:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開  讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:10:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…那個…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.55,0:10:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓小姐～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像聽到了真的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是錯覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.03,0:11:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來這是幸運肉包呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.16,0:11:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.28,0:11:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金錢運一般般
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛運馬馬虎虎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要找的人在前方3米？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.33,0:11:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  我也該回去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是呢  三浦小姐和菊地君都不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.72,0:11:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只剩你了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.81,0:11:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.48,0:11:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.19,0:11:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正待會兒也要拍她的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.06,0:11:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在三浦回來之前先拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.19,0:11:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只有這樣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.28,0:11:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快點準備一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用著急
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.57,0:12:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在梓她們回來之前  要給美希
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.49,0:12:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.92,0:12:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了  梓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什  你幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.64,0:12:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認  認錯人了  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓  你在哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.65,0:12:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不過剛才那人挺帥的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.03,0:12:47.45,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(84,125)}気楽にいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.03,0:12:47.45,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(84,125)}想輕鬆一點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:51.45,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(125,125)}でも少し気持ち揺れる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:51.45,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(125,125)}不過好像有點猶豫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.16,0:12:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥都畫不出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:55.08,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(84,125)}このままでいいのかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:55.08,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(84,125)}這樣真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.25,0:12:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有什麼能激發靈感呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:59.34,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(83,83)}そんなときは思いっきり
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:59.34,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(83,83)}這種時候  就狠狠地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:03.47,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(125,83)}深呼吸して
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:03.47,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(125,83)}深呼吸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.38,0:13:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈感來啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:11.81,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(84,83)}街は晴れ色　心も晴れて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:11.81,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(84,83)}城裡好天氣  心也好暢快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.98,0:13:14.44,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(125,84)}悩んでないで
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.98,0:13:14.44,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(125,84)}別煩惱了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:19.57,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(126,125)}美味しいもの　食べにゆこう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:19.57,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(126,125)}去找些好吃的  美美地吃一頓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.65,0:13:23.49,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(84,125)}いつもの場所で
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.65,0:13:23.49,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(84,125)}要是在老地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:27.20,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(125,126)}会えたらいいね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:27.20,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(125,126)}能見到該多好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.37,0:13:31.75,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(84,84)}探しものは見つかったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.37,0:13:31.75,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(84,84)}要找的東西  已經找到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:39.46,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(84,84)}もう大丈夫だから
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:39.46,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(84,84)}不用替我擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.75,0:13:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真頭疼啊  哪都找不到計程車站  咦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.22,0:13:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.49,0:13:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.89,0:14:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子疼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  能拜託你看下店嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.97,0:14:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得趕快點回去工作才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很擔心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  能幫我占卜一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好  那個  不過可能不準
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.05,0:14:36.27,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(83,84)}もっと 高めて果てなく 心の奥まで
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.05,0:14:36.27,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(83,84)}衝向更深的境界  直到心底
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.27,0:14:40.27,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(125,84)}あなただけが使えるテクニックで
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.27,0:14:40.27,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(125,84)}使出你獨有的舞技
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:41.94,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(83,125)}溶かしつくして
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:41.94,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(83,125)}把它徹底融化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.94,0:14:46.86,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(125,83)}本能 涡巻く最中に堕ちてくときめき
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.94,0:14:46.86,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(125,83)}本能  墮入漩渦中心的躁動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好精彩的電影啊  正好到高潮了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:51.83,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(84,84)}今宵だけの梦 踊るわ激しく
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:51.83,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(84,84)}只屬於今夜的夢  盡情地舞蹈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個演員  好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.99,0:14:54.16,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(83,125)}この身のかぎりに
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.99,0:14:54.16,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(83,125)}盡情地將這副身軀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:56.54,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(83,84)}燃やすわ激しく
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:56.54,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(83,84)}燃燒至極限吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.12,0:15:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實啊  我被跟我有婚約的女士甩掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是今天就要離開日本了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.13,0:15:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以最後想在日本找一個能留下美好回憶的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該去哪比較好
